        "text": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The name comes from <em>ephemeral</em> — a reminder that the most meaningful things in life are often the most transient. We believe the adornments you wear become quiet witnesses to those memories, letting the joy of past moments sparkle again whenever you see them.</p><p>Every curve and edge serves a deliberate purpose. We favor asymmetry, subtle tension, and forms that feel alive rather than static. Nothing is accidental, yet nothing feels forced.</p>",
            "text_font_class": "fs-body-100"
          }
        },
