        "text": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Echoes</strong> — Pearls and precious stones set in flowing organic 14k gold. Freshwater pearls, African tourmaline, moonstone, and aquamarine — nature's own treasures, held in forms inspired by tide pools, coral, and winter branches. For quiet moments and grand occasions.</p><p><strong>Draped in Time</strong> — Bold hand-painted enamel on sterling silver. Chunky organic shapes draped like fabric, alive with polka dots, marble swirls, and vivid color. Each ring is a small act of self-expression — playful, confident, and impossible to ignore.</p><p>Together, they represent every version of you.</p>",
            "text_font_class": "fs-body-100"
          }
        }
